---
/* 
  OnboardingPanel.astro
  初見ユーザーの習熟度に応じて最適な入口へ誘導するオンボーディングコンポーネント
  ChatGPT・Gemini評価フィードバックに基づく導線改善施策
*/
---

<section class="onboarding-section" id="onboarding-panel">
  <div class="onboarding-container">
    <div class="onboarding-header">
      <span class="onboarding-badge">QUICK NAVIGATION</span>
      <h2 class="onboarding-title">あなたの目的に合わせて、最短ルートをご案内します</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="onboarding-grid">
      <!-- 初めての方 -->
      <a href="/articles/antigravity-start/" class="onboarding-card card-start">
        <div class="card-accent"></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
            <span class="card-icon">🚀</span>
          </div>
          <span class="card-phase">BEGINNER</span>
          <h3 class="card-heading">AIエージェントを<br/>初めて使う方</h3>
          <p class="card-desc">環境構築から最初の成功体験まで。5分で読めるスタートガイドから始めましょう。</p>
          <div class="card-action">
            <span class="action-label">スタートガイドを読む</span>
            <span class="action-time">所要時間：約5分</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- 使い始めた方 -->
      <a href="/antigravity/hub/" class="onboarding-card card-intermediate">
        <div class="card-accent"></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
            <span class="card-icon">📡</span>
          </div>
          <span class="card-phase">SKILL UP</span>
          <h3 class="card-heading">もっと使いこなしたい方</h3>
          <p class="card-desc">散在するノウハウを4フェーズで体系化。START → USE → FIX → MASTERの最短ルートへ。</p>
          <div class="card-action">
            <span class="action-label">学習ロードマップへ</span>
            <span class="action-time">4フェーズ / 全12記事</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <!-- 壁にぶつかっている方 -->
      <a href="#diagnosis-hub" class="onboarding-card card-troubleshoot">
        <div class="card-accent"></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="card-icon-wrapper">
            <span class="card-icon">🛡️</span>
          </div>
          <span class="card-phase">FIX NOW</span>
          <h3 class="card-heading">今すぐ問題を<br/>解決したい方</h3>
          <p class="card-desc">「重い」「コードが壊れる」「情報漏洩が不安」—症状から最適な解決策を即座に提示します。</p>
          <div class="card-action">
            <span class="action-label">症状から診断する</span>
            <span class="action-time">最短30秒で解決策へ</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .onboarding-section {
    padding: 0 0 60px;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .onboarding-container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 5%;
  }

  .onboarding-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .onboarding-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #22c55e;
    padding: 5px 14px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .onboarding-title {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .onboarding-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .onboarding-card {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
  }

  .onboarding-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    border-color: transparent;
  }

  /* カード上部のアクセントライン */
  .card-accent {
    height: 3px;
    width: 100%;
    transition: height 0.4s ease;
  }

  .card-start .card-accent { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2563eb, #60a5fa); }
  .card-intermediate .card-accent { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #b8860b, #d4a843); }
  .card-troubleshoot .card-accent { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ef4444, #f87171); }

  .onboarding-card:hover .card-accent {
    height: 4px;
  }

  .card-body {
    padding: 36px 30px 32px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .card-icon-wrapper {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .card-phase {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
  }

  .card-start .card-phase { color: #2563eb; }
  .card-intermediate .card-phase { color: #b8860b; }
  .card-troubleshoot .card-phase { color: #ef4444; }

  .card-heading {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin: 0 0 14px 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .card-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .card-action {
    margin-top: 28px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .action-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .onboarding-card:hover .action-label {
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .action-time {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: #999;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* ホバー時のカードボーダー色 */
  .card-start:hover { border-color: #2563eb; }
  .card-intermediate:hover { border-color: #b8860b; }
  .card-troubleshoot:hover { border-color: #ef4444; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .onboarding-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .onboarding-card {
      flex-direction: row;
    }
    .card-accent {
      width: 3px;
      height: auto;
      min-height: 100%;
    }
    .onboarding-card:hover .card-accent {
      width: 4px;
      height: auto;
    }
    .card-body {
      padding: 24px 24px;
    }
    .card-heading {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }
    .card-heading br {
      display: none;
    }
    .card-icon-wrapper {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .card-icon {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .onboarding-title {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .card-body {
      padding: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
